basics 
to create a workspace - mkdir -p ~/workspace_name/src/
to go inside any folder cd ./
example cd ./workspace_name/src/
to create package  - catkin_create_pkg <package_name> <dependencies>
to update files - source ~/workspace_name/devel/setup.bash
after every python file make it execuitable by going into its directory using cd command and typing chmod u+x <pythonfile_name.py>
